      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes; formal SQA plan in place.",
      "rationale": "Solver is version-controlled but test suite coverage is limited to canonical benchmark cases; no hemolysis-specific regression tests documented. Achieved level 2 falls short of required level 4 for MRL 5."
