    "rationale": "Credibility assessment package accepted for archival and submission purposes. All 13 credibility factors evaluated; 7 factors assessed with achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5, and 6 factors not assessed due to epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo UQ performed on geometric inputs only. Package accepted as complete submission record notwithstanding identified credibility gaps, which are documented for regulatory review. Regulatory acceptance of the underlying device claim remains pending.",
